high_descs: Turn to the small counter
Pick up the bottle of perfume from the counter
Go to the toilet
Place the perfume on top of the toilet
Go to the bin
Take the perfume bottle out of the bin
Go to the toilet
Place the second perfume bottle next to the first perfume bottle on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Place two perfume bottles on top of a toilet

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white drawers with the wooden top.
Pick up the bottle of lotion to the left of the bar of soap.
Turn around and face the back of the toilet.
Put the lotion down on the left side of the back of the toilet.
Walk over to the blue bin to the left of the white drawers.
Pick up the bottle of lotion from the blue bin.
Turn around and walk over to the back of the toilet.
Place the bottle of lotion on the back of the toilet behind the first bottle of lotion.
anns.task_desc: To move two bottles of lotion to the back of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn around and walk toward the counter
Pick up the soap on the counter
Turn around and walk back to the toilet
Place the soap on top of the toilet
Walk around the toilet and to the wall on the left side, turn right and walk towards waste basket
Pick up soap out of waste basket
Turn around and walk back to the toilet
Place the soap on top of the toilet
anns.task_desc: Place soap on top of toilet
